{
    "info": {
        "_postman_id": "manthan-guru-policy-excel",
        "name": "Manthan Guru - Policy Excel Import/Export",
        "description": "API collection for importing policy data and exporting clients/policies",
        "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
    },
    "item": [
        {
            "name": "Authentication",
            "item": [
                {
                    "name": "Login",
                    "event": [
                        {
                            "listen": "test",
                            "script": {
                                "exec": [
                                    "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                                    "  const jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                                    "  pm.environment.set('auth_token', jsonData.token);",
                                    "  console.log('Token saved:', jsonData.token.substring(0, 20) + '...');",
                                    "}"
                                ]
                            }
                        }
                    ],
                    "request": {
                        "method": "POST",
                        "header": [
                            {
                                "key": "Content-Type",
                                "value": "application/json"
                            }
                        ],
                        "body": {
                            "mode": "raw",
                            "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"admin\",\n  \"password\": \"admin123\"\n}"
                        },
                        "url": {
                            "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/login",
                            "host": [
                                "{{base_url}}"
                            ],
                            "path": [
                                "api",
                                "auth",
                                "login"
                            ]
                        },
                        "description": "Login to get JWT token. Token is automatically saved to {{auth_token}} variable."
                    },
                    "response": []
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "name": "Policy Import/Export",
            "item": [
                {
                    "name": "Import Policy Data from Excel",
                    "event": [
                        {
                            "listen": "test",
                            "script": {
                                "exec": [
                                    "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                                    "  const response = pm.response.json();",
                                    "  console.log('\\n=== IMPORT SUMMARY ===');",
                                    "  console.log('Sheets Processed:', response.results.sheets_processed);",
                                    "  console.log('Clients Created:', response.results.clients_created);",
                                    "  console.log('Clients Updated:', response.results.clients_updated);",
                                    "  console.log('Policies Created:', response.results.policies_created);",
                                    "  console.log('Policies Updated:', response.results.policies_updated);",
                                    "  console.log('Errors:', response.results.errors);",
                                    "  console.log('\\nFirst 10 Details:');",
                                    "  response.results.details.slice(0, 10).forEach((d, i) => {",
                                    "    console.log(`${i+1}. Sheet: ${d.sheet}, Row: ${d.row}, Status: ${d.status}${d.error ? ', Error: ' + d.error : ''}`);",
                                    "  });",
                                    "}"
                                ]
                            }
                        }
                    ],
                    "request": {
                        "method": "POST",
                        "header": [
                            {
                                "key": "Authorization",
                                "value": "Bearer {{auth_token}}"
                            }
                        ],
                        "body": {
                            "mode": "formdata",
                            "formdata": [
                                {
                                    "key": "file",
                                    "type": "file",
                                    "src": "/path/to/client_data.xlsx",
                                    "disabled": false
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        "url": {
                            "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/clients/import-excel",
                            "host": [
                                "{{base_url}}"
                            ],
                            "path": [
                                "api",
                                "clients",
                                "import-excel"
                            ]
                        },
                        "description": "Upload Excel file with policy data from multiple sheets.\n\nExpected columns:\n- Assured Name / Proposar Name (client name)\n- Mobile (client phone, unique key)\n- Policy Number / Policy No. (policy ID)\n- Due Date, Premium, Sum Insured (optional)\n\nProcess:\n1. Click 'Select File' and choose your client_data.xlsx\n2. Make sure auth_token is set (login first)\n3. Send the request\n4. Review the summary in console output\n\nResponse includes:\n- Clients created/updated\n- Policies created/updated\n- Detailed breakdown of what happened"
                    },
                    "response": []
                },
                {
                    "name": "Export Clients & Policies",
                    "event": [
                        {
                            "listen": "test",
                            "script": {
                                "exec": [
                                    "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                                    "  console.log('Export successful - file downloaded');",
                                    "}"
                                ]
                            }
                        }
                    ],
                    "request": {
                        "method": "GET",
                        "header": [
                            {
                                "key": "Authorization",
                                "value": "Bearer {{auth_token}}"
                            }
                        ],
                        "url": {
                            "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/clients/export",
                            "host": [
                                "{{base_url}}"
                            ],
                            "path": [
                                "api",
                                "clients",
                                "export"
                            ]
                        },
                        "description": "Export all clients and policies as Excel file.\n\nOutput file has 2 sheets:\n1. Clients - ID, Name, Phone, Email, Address, Created Date\n2. Policies - Client Name, Phone, Policy Number, Insurance Company, Premium, Sum Insured, Dates, Status\n\nFile will be auto-downloaded with format: clients_policies_YYYY-MM-DD.xlsx\n\nTo use:\n1. Send the request\n2. Postman will download the file\n3. File appears in your Downloads folder"
                    },
                    "response": []
                },
                {
                    "name": "Get All Policies with Client Details",
                    "event": [
                        {
                            "listen": "test",
                            "script": {
                                "exec": [
                                    "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                                    "  const response = pm.response.json();",
                                    "  console.log('\\n=== POLICIES SUMMARY ===');",
                                    "  console.log('Total Policies:', response.total);",
                                    "  console.log('\\nFirst 5 Policies:');",
                                    "  response.policies.slice(0, 5).forEach((p, i) => {",
                                    "    console.log(`${i+1}. ID: ${p.id}, Policy#: ${p.policy_number}, Client: ${p.client_name}, Provider: ${p.provider}, Premium: ${p.premium_amount}`);",
                                    "  });",
                                    "  console.log('\\n[Scroll down to see all policies in response body]');",
                                    "}"
                                ]
                            }
                        }
                    ],
                    "request": {
                        "method": "GET",
                        "header": [
                            {
                                "key": "Authorization",
                                "value": "Bearer {{auth_token}}"
                            }
                        ],
                        "url": {
                            "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/policies/all-with-details",
                            "host": [
                                "{{base_url}}"
                            ],
                            "path": [
                                "api",
                                "policies",
                                "all-with-details"
                            ]
                        },
                        "description": "Get all policies with complete client details for data verification.\n\nReturns:\n- Total count of all policies\n- Complete policy information (ID, number, type, premium, dates, status, etc.)\n- Associated client details (name, phone, email, address)\n\nUseful for:\n- Verifying policy-client relationships\n- Checking data consistency\n- Identifying discrepancies\n- Auditing imported data\n- Ensuring no orphaned policies\n\nEach policy record includes:\n- policy_id, client_id, policy_number, policy_type\n- provider, premium_amount, sum_assured\n- start_date, end_date, status\n- client_name, client_phone, client_email, client_address"
                    },
                    "response": []
                }
            ]
        },
